018\">https://doi.org/10.1016/j.chb.2016.01.018</a>.</p><p class=\"c-article-references__links u-hide-print\"><a data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"outbound reference\" data-track-label=\"link\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.chb.2016.01.018\" aria-label=\"Article reference 47\">Article</a>\u00a0", "    <a data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"outbound reference\" data-track-label=\"link\" aria-label=\"Google Scholar reference 47\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?&amp;title=An%20inclusive%20design%20approach%20for%20developing%20video%20games%20for%20children%20with%20autism%20spectrum%20disorder&amp;journal=Computers%20in%20Human%20Behavior&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.chb.2016.01.018&amp;volume=71&amp;pages=535-549&amp;publication_year=2017&amp;author=Malinverni%2CL&amp;author=Mora-Guiard%2CJ&amp;author=Padillo%2CV&amp;author=Valero%2CL&amp;author=Hervas%2CA&amp;author=Pares%2CN\">", "                    Google Scholar</a>\u00a0", "                </p></li><li class=\"c-article-references__item js-c-reading-companion-references-item\"><p class=\"c-article-references__text\" id=\"ref-CR49\">Malinverni, L., Mora-Guiard, J., &amp; Pares, N. (2016). Towards methods for evaluating and communicating participatory design: A multimodal approach. <i>International Journal of Human\u2014Computer Studies</i>, <i>94</i>(53\u201363), 004. <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijhcs.2016.03\">https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijhcs.2016.03</a>.</p><p class=\"c-article-references__links u-hide-print\"><a data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"outbound reference\" data-track-label=\"link\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1016%2Fj.ijhcs.2016.03\" aria-label=\"Article reference 48\">Article</a>\u00a0", "    <a data-track=\"click\" data-track-action=\"outbound reference\" data-track-label=\"link\" aria-label=\"Google Scholar reference 48\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?&amp;title=Towards%20methods%20for%20evaluating%20and%20communicating%20participatory%20desi